# Scraper working artifact: the paginated register index is re-fetched fresh at
# the start of every scrape run and only used within that run to derive matter
# links. It changes on every fetch (session token / ordering) even when no
# merger data has changed, so committing it just adds noise.
data/raw/acquisitions-register.html
